[_Technology: US authorities survey AI ecosystem through antitrust lens_](https://www.ibanet.org/technology-us-authorities-survey-ai-ecosystem-through-antitrust-lens) William Roberts, IBA US Correspondent Friday 2 August 2024 Antitrust authorities in the US are targeting the new frontier of artificial intelligence (AI) for potential enforcement action. &hellip;
